>Tire Compatibility</strong></p><ul><li>Wheel and tire compatibility: 27.5″ x 2.6″ or 29″ x 2.6″ (depending on tire/rim manufacturer)</li><li>Frame max spacing: 78mm</li><li>Fork max spacing: 78mm</li></ul><p><strong>Brake Compatibility</strong></p><ul><li>Post-mount brakes: 180mm max front rotor / 160mm max rear rotor</li></ul><p><strong>Details</strong></p><ul><li>Sizes: S / M / L / XL</li><li>Frame weight: 2400g (size L – w/o thru-axle)</li><li>Fork weight: 1125g (with uncut steerer&nbsp;/ not including axle)</li><li>Color: Sierra Red</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://us.ritcheylogic.com/us_en/ascent-frameset?goal=0_a8437982ed-886ab0832a-227396845\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>ritcheylogic.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a815d2991e67881baed1386509acf4947b3da95919f181dcf28769294c022325","category":"Cycling"}